South Africa’s Mminele Says Risks to ‘Difficult’ Economic Recovery Large

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-05-27T06:16:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/south-africa-s-mminele-says-risks-to-difficult-economic-recovery-large.html
 South African Deputy Governor  Daniel
Mminele  said risks to the country’s “difficult” economic
recovery remain large with the global environment being so
uncertain.  Central banks need to find ways of dealing with inflation
without jeopardizing the economic recovery, he said in a speech
in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
